SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDateTime], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ComparisonId], [t0].[Cost], [t0].[Description], [t0].[FavoriteId], [t0].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDateTime], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Amount], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[ProductId], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ComparisonId], [p].[Cost], [p].[Description], [p].[FavoriteId], [p].[Name]
    FROM [CartLines] AS [c0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]
